{"tid":259492,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"萬花筒寫輪眼定輪迴眼勁？","createTime":"2017-05-27T03:34:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-27T04:32:45.000Z","uid":86587,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0d5683853e49c850c61e3bb89b53bbed64cdedee","tid":259492,"uid":86587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T03:34:50.000Z","msg":"萬花筒寫輪眼最勁應該係雙神威，攻防無敵<br />\n<br />\n輪迴眼招數比較多，最實用應該係吸收忍術，唔係既話斑早就比塵遁分解，但係吸咗仙人查克拉會中伏變青蛙<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有地爆天星威力無窮，可以一次過封印9隻尾獸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過威力都好睇用既係長門定斑。<br />\n至於天手力只係弱版飛雷神，不值一哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n輪墓我到依家都唔太明個原理<br />\n<br />\n大家覺得邊對眼勁D？<br />\n<br />\n萬花筒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n輪迴眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e73cc49ff7de2862ced10f6992f6bede3473715","tid":259492,"uid":25612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T03:37:40.000Z","msg":"輪墓係一個對方睇唔到打唔到嘅分身術"},{"pid":"885e1186af407dbf3677d4d16b89e0aa958f2411","tid":259492,"uid":58512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T03:38:04.000Z","msg":"一招輪墓屌打全部"},{"pid":"224a106299cb10c6f7e0ac3399bc1592deb430c7","tid":259492,"uid":25612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T03:40:38.000Z","msg":"其實輪墓穿唔穿得過須佐能乎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d5f1596f01f8d44172360b809ebc49a43f20f22","tid":259492,"uid":22971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T03:40:54.000Z","msg":"點解成日都要問依啲問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"feca270406e09a6cce9f3ee4bc400141223989c8","tid":259492,"uid":11055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T04:32:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實輪墓穿唔穿得過須佐能乎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hk